OL,7,FA carer who stole money from her
OL,8,Fclients to pay off a car loan and fund
OL,9,FBotox treatment has been jailed.
OL,11,FBetween November 2017 and February
OL,12,F2019, Donna Mullady stole more than
OL,13,F#30,000 from three elderly victims,
OL,14,Fwhilst she was working as a carer for
OL,15,Fvulnerable and elderly adults.
OL,17,FHer victims were men aged 59, 82 and
OL,18,F91.
