OL,7,FWhile food shopping for the men, which
OL,8,Fthey could not do themselves, the 49-
OL,9,Fyear-old would withdraw cash and
OL,10,Fdeposit into her own bank account.
OL,12,FShe used the victims' bank cards at
OL,13,Fretail stores they wouldn't typically
OL,14,Fgo to, like Primark, New Look and JD
OL,15,FSports.
OL,17,FMullady also used their money to pay
OL,18,Foff a car loan, phone contract, Botox
OL,19,Ftreatment and holidays like Thailand,
OL,20,FBarbados and skiing.
