OL,7,FMullady was sentenced to 32 months in
OL,8,Fprison at Reading Crown Court on 15
OL,9,FJuly.
OL,11,FShe previously pleaded guilty to three
OL,12,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,13,Frepresentation at the same court on
OL,14,FMonday 13 May.
OL,16,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,17,FConstable Rachel Pithers said: "I am
OL,18,Fextremely pleased that Mullady has
OL,19,Fbeen given a custodial sentence
OL,20,Ffollowing what was a long and complex
OL,21,Finvestigation.
